Manufacturing companies have built a flexible production system that responds to market demand by collecting real-time data 
and analyzing and utilizing it through AI. As a result, they have succeeded in enhancing competitiveness by improving efficiency, product quality, and providing customized products. 
They have also implemented initiatives for predictive maintenance and safety assurance by combining real-time sensor data with AI analysis and utilization. 
The use of data and AI in manufacturing has evolved with the changing times, and it is now transforming the fundamentals of manufacturing processes and business strategies.
